                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/16380891/" class="">第44页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/srada/" class=" " title="阿特米斯雷宣">阿特米斯雷宣</a>
                (Admin law is not for sissies)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="16380891">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">诗有律而诗亡，词有谱而词衰，汉魏古风、北宋小令，其卓绝处不能以格律绳之者。至于学究咏诗，经生填词，了无性灵，遑论境界。造园之道，消息相通。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-01-25 09:06</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>诗有律而诗亡，词有谱而词衰，汉魏古风、北宋小令，其卓绝处不能以格律绳之者。至于学究咏诗，经生填词，了无性灵，遑论境界。造园之道，消息相通。</q></blockquote>
